LanguageData.LingCHAutoCLD: The heater will automatically adjust the efficiency. Due to the limitation of sensors, the response speed of adjustment is not as fast as manual adjustment. \nWarning: Do not turn on auto mode outdoors.
LanguageData.LingCHEffectDownD: Reduce heater efficiency while saving energy.
LanguageData.LingCHEffectUpD: Improve the efficiency of the heater, which will increase power consumption.
